Content:: Nieder-Eschbach is a borough (Ortsbezirk) of Frankfurt am Main, Germany. After 1465 Nieder-Eschbach belonged to the Archbishopric of Mainz. Ecclesiastical Middle Authority was the Archdeacon of the provost of St. Peter in Mainz.
